Adding images (2 ways to add images : 1) from local assets, 2) from internet via URL's)
. first of all, edit pubspec.yaml file flutter > assets section
. then click on "Pub get" on top
1) Local asset images :
 - Image.asset(...)
 - Image(image: AssetImage("Path/To/Image"))

2) Remote network images :
 - Image.network(...)
 - Image(image: NetworkImage("https://www..../chacecomlogo.png")

 ---------------------------------------------------
 Adding icons (2 types)
 1) Material icons (provided by default in flutter):

 2) FontAwesome icons (need dependency installation):
    - go to www.pub.dev packages
    - identify the package needed
    - go to installation section
    - copy the snippet & paste in project's "pubspec" file
    - press "pub get" to install the dependency ! OK


Icons didn't load::
- terminate app
- Menu : tools > flutter > Flutter clean
- then tools > flutter > Flutter pub get